func main() {
	logContent := `Task iteration 1: audit
The agent tool calls a command and then calls a helper.
Tool call prose says to retry since the command can call another action.
The agent is calling to check for misuse on unified output.
A sentence with using tool language should not create with or tool entries.
● startHttpServer
● noop
● label_agent
● Read workflow prompt and agent output files (shell)
Tool call: explicit_legacy
Executing tool: explicitExec
Calling: explicit_call
Using tool: explicit_use
`
